data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful farmhouse style is a spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath with over 2000 Square feet with lovely rustic charm. This house sits on a 1.5 acre lot in a highly sought after neighborhood in Caddo Mills, Texas. In the cold months, keep warm with the real wood log burning stone fireplace and enjoy summer evenings on the covered porch or early morning coffee while watching the sun rise.
